I was just looking for a good Caesar's salad.
The ambience is severely lacking.
The fact that the restaurant is not cordoned off from the main casino floor makes for a smoky, unpleasant experience.
If you don't like smoke, I would suggest you attempt to be seated as far away from the slot machines as possible.
