Most of the time if they are made in house they are awful and fall apart.
This one was fantastic!
Great flavor and texture.
Great bun and cheese and I added a fried egg...perfection.
Will go to the smelly casino just to get another burger!Worth the price.
Great French fries also.
My meat eating family was all happy with their burgers too!

